# This file could be used for testing the API with Visual Studio Code


## Retrieve all the posts
GET http://localhost:3001/api/posts HTTP/1.1
###

## Retrieve a single post by ID
GET http://localhost:3001/api/posts/4 HTTP/1.1
###

## Create a new post (auth required)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/posts HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "This is an amazing post!",
  "text": "Post body",
  "max_comments": 5
}


